        <label>Figure 1</label>
        <caption>
          <p>Workflow for creating NetGenes database. The initial 27 interactomes were used as the training dataset to build the machine learning (ML) model. The 2711 interactomes were run through the ML model to obtain the essential gene predictions. These predictions are curated and published in the “NetGenes” database.</p>
        </caption>
